1 (3) The amount of the allowance for the support of additional children
2 living in a parent’s home described in § 12–201(c)(1)(iii) of this subtitle shall be subtracted
3 from the parent’s actual income before the court determines the amount of a child support
4 award.
5 SECTION 2. AND BE IT FURTHER ENACTED, That this Act shall take effect
6 October 1, 2026.

